  "2026-06-07T13:01:27.334Z",codex-active-pm-cycle-20260607,"Full verification stack passed on branch: pnpm build; pnpm typecheck; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (2554 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines); pnpm contracts:check; pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; pnpm audit --audit-level low; node scripts/release/compatibility-check.mjs --json (ok true, item_count_before=2 item_count_after=2); node scripts/release/sentry-telemetry-gate.mjs --json --telemetry-mode best-effort (critical=0, high=0, telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=2.06, missing_error_code_rows=0). Manual temp smoke also verified MCP ping returns empty result and runtime gc removes history-drift-cache.json."
